'''Caenorhabditis elegans Cer13 virus''' is a species of virus in the genus ''[[Semotivirus]]'' and the family [[Belpaoviridae]]. It exists as [[retrotransposon]]s in the ''[[Caenorhabditis elegans]]'' genome.

