inkichi Horiba|jp|堀場信吉}}, [[Yasujiro Niwa]] (27th)<ref name="21st-30th"/> * 1936 &mdash; {{ill|Hisayosi Ogawa|jp|小川尚義}}, [[Takaoki Sasaki]], [[Tomizo Yoshida]] (26th)<ref name="21st-30th"/> * 1935 &mdash; {{ill|Shimpei Ogura|jp|小倉進平}}, {{ill|Shinsho Hanayama|jp|花山信勝}} (25th)<ref name="21st-30th"/> * 1934 &mdash; [[Noboru Niida]], {{ill|Seitaro Tsuboi|jp|坪井誠太郎}} (24th)<ref name="21st-30th"/> * 1933 &mdash; {{ill|Ziro Tuzi|jp|辻二郎}}, [[Bunsuke Suzuki]] (23rd)<ref name="21st-30th"/> * 1932 &mdash; [[Kyōsuke Kindaichi]], [[Kiyoo Wadati]] (22nd)<ref name="21st-30th"/> * 1931 &mdash; {{ill|Katsutada Sezawa|de|}} (21st)<ref name="21st-30th"/> * 1930 &mdash; {{ill|Buntaro Adachi|jp|足立文太郎}} (20th)<ref name="11th-20th">Japan Academy, [http://www.japan-acad.go.jp/en/activities/jyusho/011to020.html 11th-20th]; retrieved 2011-08-15</ref> * 1929 &mdash; {{ill|Toshi Shida|jp|志田順}} (19th)<ref name="11th-20th"/> * 1928 &mdash; {{ill|Masao Kambe|jp|神戸正雄}}, [[Sōichi Kakeya]] (18th)<ref name="11th-20th"/> * 1927 &mdash; {{ill|Shigeru Kato|jp|加藤繁}}, {{ill|Yuji Shibata|de|}} (17th)<ref name="11th-20th"/> * 1926 &mdash; {{ill|Yorisuke Numata|jp|沼田頼輔}}, {{ill|Yoshiaki Ozawa|jp|小沢儀明}} (16th)<ref name="11th-20th"/> * 1925 &mdash; {{ill|Keiki Yabuki|jp|矢吹慶輝}}, {{ill|Nagaho Mononobe|jp|物部長穂}} (15th)<ref name="11th-20th"/> * 1924 &mdash; {{ill|Kuniji Yashiro|jp|八代国治}}, [[Takaoki Sasaki]] (14th)<ref name="11th-20th"/> * 1923 &mdash; [[Tokutomi Sohō|Iichiro Tokutomi]], [[Shigematsu Kakimura]], {{ill|Yasuhiko Asahina|de|}}, [[Suekichi Kinoshita]] (13th)<ref name="11th-20th"/> * 1922 &mdash; [[Toshio Takamine]], {{ill|Usaburo Yoshida|jp|吉田卯三郎}} (12th)<ref name="11th-20th"/> * 1921 &mdash; {{ill|Zennosuke Tsuji|jp|辻善之助}}, [[Gennosuke Fuse]] (11th)<ref name="11th-20th"/> * 1920 &mdash; {{ill|Kaneyuki Miura|jp|三浦周行}}, [[Mitsumaru Tsujimoto]] (10th)<ref name="1st-10th">Japan Academy, [http://www.japan-acad.go.jp/en/activities/jyusho/001to010.html#anker001 1st-10th]; retrieved 2011-08-15</ref> * 1919 &md