==Space Pods==
In 2015 TMRO began producing Space Pods, which are short videos about various space-related topics. Space Pods are typically presented by either Michael Clark or Jared Head, with others occasionally presenting, including Benjamin Higginbotham and Tim Dodd. Lisa Stojanovski and Ariel Waldman formerly hosted Space Pods.

==Other shows==
===TMRO Science===
